divs: Sighting DetailsMy husband & I left a restaurant near Scranton PA, on the way home from upstate NY, & noticed a very very very bright star. It seemed to have moved around in the same area for about 5 minutes or so. It did not appear to be an airplane or a helicopter...it was way too high up. I was intrigued enough to take some photos of it, which I have enclosed.
Summary: Looked like a VERY bright star, but moved around in small area for about 5 minutes.
